potential of current and future studies using\nrapid-response, targeted numerical-relativity simulations for better\nunderstanding gravitational-wave observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jul 2016 02:21:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-22"}
