fective number of species around 0.4 would reconcile the CMB-inferred\nconstraints, and the local $H_0$ and standard ruler determinations. The\ninclusion of the \"preliminary\" high-l Planck CMB polarisation data disfavours\nthis solution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jul 2016 14:55:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2016 11:40:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-21"}
